{"_id":"7DKjYkkuhjwk7l2y","name":"Prosthetics","content":"<p>Whether through disease, warfare, or misfortune, it’s a relatively common occurrence in the Empire to lose body parts. For those who do, there are a variety of alternatives on offer. All Prosthetics have an Encumbrance of 0 when worn.</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Item</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Cost</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Enc</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Availability</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.1H8pOSNxRS69PADr]{Eye patch}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">6d</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Common</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.wVL0ugPXCBLGzdNm]{False Eye}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1GC</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Rare</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.lJ6Av6wQfORR4mnu]{False Leg}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">16/-</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Scarce</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.qDEu30xKhIxfSckg]{Gilded Nose}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">18/-</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Scarce</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.YivL32R2L3J098VD]{Hook}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">3/4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Common</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.KGW0J62iYLqRIfS4]{Engineering Marvel}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">20GC</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Exotic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.trappings.0ohrc7pJtVTo9IFk]{Wooden Teeth}</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">10/-</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Rare</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","img":null,"folder":"BrtIycD1u7HxITud","sort":700000,"permission":{"default":2,"uZJKPuqDv0BBLk9c":3,"VnnpieLwbiAu3Owf":3,"hNHeJbKl47AOkoOO":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.VBJm4TlfiskokRqI"},"wfrp4e":{"initialization-folder":"Trapping Lists"},"wfrp4e-core":{"initialization-folder":"Trapping Lists","sort":1300001}}}
{"_id":"7OPjxAxjOdhthxLp","name":"ANGESTAG","content":"<h1 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">ANGESTAG </h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">In the <strong>SQUARE OF MARTIALS</strong> from the 11th hour before noon</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a62937c8-7fff-bcf7-000a-9574a80955ab\"></span></p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">An Open Ice Rink for Amateurs</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">At the <strong>BERNABAU STADIUM</strong></p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">THE SNOTBALL FINAL </h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">from the 2nd hour </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">In the <strong>GREAT PARK</strong></p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">The Pageant and Jousting</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">from the 2nd hour until the 6th after noon</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Followed by the renowned</p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Black Pool Illuminations</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">from the 9th hour after noon</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">In <strong>THE ROYAL COLLEGE OF MUSIC</strong></p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Giuseppe Pastrami’s </h3>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Luccinian Liturgical Castrates Choir</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">from the 2nd hour after noon</p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">“The Ring of the Nibble Unger Lied, Part I”</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">from the 6th hour after noon to midnight</p>","folder":"LaUWtwaJi9qsofyf","sort":787500,"permission":{"default":2,"hNHeJbKl47AOkoOO":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7RHiP1TKCbrkEu5u","name":"Fleishmark","permission":{"default":2,"hNHeJbKl47AOkoOO":3},"folder":"WQm4k9MEuHY8Q0Ct","sort":100000,"flags":{},"content":"<p>In the midst of the East End, the Fleishmark district deals almost exclusively in the slaughter of animals and the processing of their meat. Every morning, drovers from farms and pastures around the Reikland queue at the east gate, hoping to gain entry to the city before the boom of the artillery fields starts up.</p>\n<p>Once through the gates, they make to the holding pens and knacker&rsquo;s yards of the Fleishmark, either to sell their livestock or see them rendered down into meat and bones. There are many odoriferous businesses in the area, such as tanneries and glue factories, making efficient use of the waste products of slaughter.</p>\n<p>A thick layer of blood and manure besmirches the cobbles, and disease breeds in the tightly packed tenements that line the alleyways nearby.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Locations</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Market Square</li>\n<li>Rumsters' Production Haus</li>\n<li>Office of the Butchers' Guild</li>\n<li>The Sewer Atrium</li>\n<li>Paeter Kohl Saddlemaker and Armourer</li>\n<li>Gluttongut's Delikatessen</li>\n</ul>"}
