{"_id":"DL3pCvWsVuA6uVXf","name":"Harvest Endeavours","content":"<h2>Keep Watch</h2>\n<p>With a successful <strong>Challenging (+0) Perception</strong> Test, the Characters may not be Surprised during that watch.</p>\n<h2>Harvest</h2>\n<p>Outdoor Survival</p>\n<h2>Warm Up</h2>\n<p>Recover from Exposure</p>\n<h2>Encourage</h2>","folder":"prP1hk4myftQ3oq7","sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"hNHeJbKl47AOkoOO":3},"flags":{}}
