{"_id":"g8XwVHgUq50VPvaC","name":"Guilds & Organisations","content":"<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Guilds &amp; Organisations</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Middenland Farmers' Association....................................................................................36 Ost Weg, Altmarkt</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Merchants' Guild...............................................................................................42 Sudetenweg, Brotkopfs</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Vittalers' Guild.......................................................................................................61 Eisenbahn, Kaufseit</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Mercers' Guild.........................................................................................................62 Eisenbahn, Kaufseit</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Gaffers' Guild.................................................................................63 Garten Weg, Kleinmoot (Altmarkt)</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Blessed Guild of Water Caddies............................................................................68 Burgen Bahn, Neumarkt</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Imperial School of Engineers Offices....................................................................75 Tempel Bahn, Nordgarten</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Guildhall of the Apothecaries......................................................................83 Todmann Allee, Ostwald</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Ratters' Guild.................................................................................................84 Hoffen Strasse, Ostwald</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Guild of Physicians....................................................................................96 Zellaut Strasse, Ulricsmund</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Middenland Miners' Guild......................................................................98 Heilige Strasse, Ulricsmund</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Dwarven Engineer's Guild...............................................................................103 Wendenbahn, The Wynd</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Guild of Stonemasons and Architects...............................................................103 Wendenbahn, The Wynd</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Wizards' and Alchemists' Guild.....................................................................45 Zauber Strasse, Freiburg</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Worshipful Guild of Legalists.................................................................................37 Markt Weg, Altmarkt</p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Charitable Organisations</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tears of Pity Mission.............................................................................62 Glockengiesserstrasse, Kaufseit</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Winter's Haven Orphanage..................................................................................77 Ost Mauer Weg, Nordtor</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Shallyan Mercyhouse............................................................................................84 Schwartz Mauer, Ostwald</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Labourers' Hospice............................................................................................94 Guntharstrasse, Sudtor</p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Private Clubs</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Blitzbeil Lodge.........................................................................................................55 Kaisergasse, Grafsmund</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Pit Fighter's Head............................................................................................................59 The Great Park</p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\">Education</h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Collegium Theologica..........................................................................................44 Palast Strasse, Freiburg</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Wizards' and Alchemists' Guild.....................................................................45 Zauber Strasse, Freiburg</p>","folder":"sz66qtwH0H7J0cc6","sort":0,"permission":{"default":2,"hNHeJbKl47A