{"_id":"wRMwk1UqH6b078Wp","name":"Note in the Cellar","content":"<p>My Dearest Stefan</p>\n<p>How much I have missed you. How much longer can we keep up the pretence? One day we will surely be uncovered. I hardly dare see you when you visit for fear that the look in my eyes will reveal the love in my heart. Can you not see the way I tremble when our hands meet in greeting, do my eyes not follow you when-</p>","folder":"prP1hk4myftQ3oq7","sort":200000,"permission":{"default":0,"hNHeJbKl47AOkoOO":3},"flags":{}}
