{"_id":"xmPfu7xoYMZzSiFJ","name":"Class Endeavors","content":"<p>Class Endeavours tend to be simpler than General Endeavours and often offer benefits more suited to characters in specific Classes. Any character can undertake any Class Endeavour, but if you don’t currently belong to the Classes specified under the Endeavour, any Tests you take are one Difficulty Level harder — so, Hard (–20) instead of Difficult (–10), for example.</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[JgPQJkjDuaDgeVv8]{Combat Training}</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[oHP1DRALXWzndRVA]{Foment Dissent}</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[ZC5clbP2pIVTdHvB]{The Latest News}</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[l8IyB9dmA3JUdFRN]{Reputation}</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[0JMJutkdH6iuxSp5]{Research Lore}</p>\n<p>@JournalEntry[uSNh8jCvDUH6Bf0Q]{Study a Mark}</p>","folder":"zQRDhzWh9uTwnQqe","sort":100001,"permission":{"default":2,"uZJKPuqDv0BBLk9c":3,"VnnpieLwbiAu3Owf":3,"hNHeJbKl47AOkoOO":3},"flags":{"wfrp4e":{"initialization-folder":"Class Endeavours"},"wfrp4e-core":{"initialization-folder":"Class Endeavours","sort":100001}}}
